{"tid":2192733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲女慘遭警撞飛騎身膝壓案與[[迦南書院 學生半裸墮樓案]]","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:53:06.000Z","uid":26770,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"747da2e6976b7097c74e8dafab10c51f7c89c2f6","tid":2192733,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"12歲女慘遭警撞飛騎身膝壓案&gt;多位不願具名的骨科醫生表示，當時警員的行為很有機會弄斷女童的肋骨、腰骨甚或脊椎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n迦南書院 學生<strong>半裸墮樓竟然查都完全唔查列自殺收隊</strong><br />\n打爆人肋骨、腰骨甚或脊椎明知受害人會終生傷殘<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">最好的掩飾方法係扔落街滅口</span>"},{"pid":"95f74af37ff2fc315d9fbb9e5c4a33c44b2bdd9a","tid":2192733,"uid":197005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d579ebaad0cf172a315e3c0f7205dc162e17601","tid":2192733,"uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1743659/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1743659/page/1</a><br />\n相關討論<br />\n<br />\n另一個可能性<br />\n性侵/拉扯時撕破受害人上衣所以<ins>扔左避免引人懷疑</ins><br />\n牛仔褲相對堅固所以無事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自殺案好少會脫光自己<br />\n9成係謀殺<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">而特快收隊唔查一定係明知自己伙記做</span>"},{"pid":"728c932d9887f210869a941f16f14b8c62e7603b","tid":2192733,"uid":75591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都合理"},{"pid":"031dd946a04453681005b00d03cddec9de736b6a","tid":2192733,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d579ebaad0cf172a315e3c0f7205dc162e17601","tid":2192733,"uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1743659/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1743659/page/1</a><br />\n相關討論<br />\n<br />\n另一個可能性<br />\n性侵/拉扯時撕破受害人上衣所以<ins>扔左避免引人懷疑</ins><br />\n牛仔褲相對堅固所以無